snippet.title: FATE: Reawakened Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Reawaken the critically acclaimed FATE games like never before! Play all 4 classic dungeon crawler titles with enhanced graphics as you battle through challenging procedurally generated dungeons, learn powerful spells, and fish to your heart’s content. Are you up to the task? Your FATE awaits!
 
Wishlist Now on Steam and Epic Games Store!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3030720/FATE_Reawakened/
Epic Games Store: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/fate-reawakened-dab2fa
Official Discord: https://discord.gg/2cWbJUTE9u
Official Website: https://playfate.com/
